<span id="freeTextContainer5881304806966622936">Mr. Ives’ Christmas is both heartbreaking and heartwarming story told during various Christmases throughout Mr. Ives life. It is a book about love, loss, faith, and forgiveness. It had me questioning my own beliefs about certain issues and understanding.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


