        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3693074852" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11770049730127011485">Not your usual Christmas story, but one of Mr Ives struggling with his sons death due to needless violence in 1950’s New York City at Christmas time. This is not an easy or joyful holiday read but a very literary slice of religious life with a protagonist who might be compared loosely with John Williams’ Stoner or maybe even Updike’s Rabbit. 3.5 stars</span>

          </span>
        </div>


